verbose_text: Since the levels of mature miRNA (miR-HBV or mutant miR HBV) and gRNA3 carrying flanking sequence of anti-HBV pri-miR-31 mimic were almost equal between 3-H38-2 and 3-M38-2 ternary cassettes, the transcription efficiencies of ternary cassette and the processing of pri-miRNA were similar between these two ternary cassettes.
